<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        section {
            padding: 50px 20px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .about, .projects, .contact {
            background: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .project-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
        }

        .project {
            width: 300px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .project img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media(max-width: 768px) {
            .project-list {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .project {
                width: 90%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>John Doe</h1>
        <p>Frontend Developer | Web Designer</p>
        <nav>
            <a href="#about">About</a>
            <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section id="about" class="about">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>Hello! I am a passionate web developer with experience in creating responsive, user-friendly websites. I love coding, designing interfaces, and learning new technologies to improve my skills.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="projects" class="projects">
        <h2>My Projects</h2>
        <div class="project-list">
            <div class="project">
                <img src="project1.jpg" alt="Project 1">
                <h3>Project One</h3>
                <p>A responsive website built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project">
                <img src="project2.jpg" alt="Project 2">
                <h3>Project Two</h3>
                <p>An e-commerce site with integrated payment system.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project">
                <img src="project3.jpg" alt="Project 3">
                <h3>Project Three</h3>
                <p>A blog platform with user authentication and content management.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="contact">
        <h2>Contact Me</h2>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:johndoe@example.com">johndoe@example.com</a></p>
        <p>LinkedIn: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/johndoe" target="_blank">linkedin.com/in/johndoe</a></p>
        <p>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/johndoe" target="_blank">github.com/johndoe</a></p>
    </section>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2026 John Doe. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
